properties.SQL:
SELECT o.*,
       e.m_sapmotortype_b1000,
       e.m_ratedpowerkw_b1004,
       e.m_insulationclass_b1021,
       e.m_dutycycle_b1012,
       e.m_voltage_b1010,
       e.m_speed1_b1067,
       e.m_framesize_b1001,
       e.m_powercode_b1002,
       e.m_poles_b1003       
FROM original o
    LEFT OUTER JOIN enrichment e
        ON 1 = 1
           AND e.m_motorproductname = o.m_motorproductname
           AND e.m_efficiencyclass_b1019 = o.m_efficiencyclass_b1019
           AND e.m_frequency_b1011 = o.m_frequency_b1011
